he key details: Founded: 2021 by Nils Schneider and Raul Kaevand Revenue Growth: From $0 (2021) → $2.4M (2022) → $20M (2024) Team Size: 15 employees (bootstrapped, no external funding) Customers: 2,900+ clients Core Product: All-in-one outreach platform with AI-powered automation, high deliverability, and built-in lead database Company Culture: Remote-first, \"no managers, no corporate BS,\" focus on shipping fast and building cutting-edge features Source: GetLatka Company Profile Detailed Job Descriptions & Requirements 1. Head of Growth Category\tDetails Core Responsibilities\t• Define and execute strategies across demand generation, partnerships, product-led growth, and user engagement • Develop and lead end-to-end growth roadmap (acquisition, activation, retention, upsell) • Scale pipelines from mid-market to enterprise • Own and accelerate go-to-market engine Key Requirements\t• Experience with growth or marketing leadership at SaaS company • Proven track record scaling pipelines from mid-market to enterprise • Deep expertise across paid media, SEO, content, PLG, and partnerships • Excellent communication skills and ability to align cross-functional teams • Experience with AI & automation tools Expected Input\tGrowth strategy, market expansion plans, partnership development Expected Output\tIncreased revenue, expanded market reach, optimized customer acquisition Strategic Rationale\tCompany growing 733% YoY needs experienced growth leader to scale systematically 2. Account Executive Category\tDetails Core Responsibilities\t• Own full sales cycle from outbound to close • Run 8-12 product demos daily • Launch own outbound campaigns to fill pipeline • Collaborate with product, engineering, and marketing teams • Work closely with founders Key Requirements\t• Proven track record in B2B sales, ideally in tech/AI sector • Strong knowledge of AI products and business applications • Experience with sales processes and CRM systems • Ability to run high-volume demo schedules • Self-starter who can generate own leads Expected Input\tLead qualification, product demonstrations, pipeline management Expected Output\tClosed deals, revenue targets, customer relationships Strategic Rationale\tFast-growing company needs scalable sales execution to support 733% growth 10 High-Impact Articles to Position Your Expertise For Head of Growth Position: Article Title\tStrategic Positioning\tKey Value Proposition \"The 4-Phase Growth Framework That Took My SaaS From $0 to $10M ARR\"\tDemonstrates systematic growth experience\tShows proven methodology for scaling SaaS companies \"Why 90% of Product-Led Growth Strategies Fail (And How to Fix Them)\"\tPositions you as PLG expert\tAddresses critical growth challenge for SaaS companies \"The AI-Powered Growth Stack: 15 Tools That 10x Your Marketing ROI\"\tShows AI/automation expertise\tAligns with company's AI focus and tool requirements \"From Startup to Scale-Up: How I Built a $50M Pipeline in 18 Months\"\tDemonstrates pipeline scaling ability\tDirectly addresses key job requirement \"The Partnership Playbook: How Strategic Alliances Drive 40% of B2B Growth\"\tShows partnership development skills\tAddresses growth channel diversification \"Data-Driven Growth: How I Increased Customer LTV by 300% Using These Metrics\"\tDemonstrates analytical approach\tShows retention and upsell expertise \"The Future of B2B Growth: Why Email Automation is Just the Beginning\"\tIndustry thought leadership\tPositions you as forward-thinking in their space \"Growth at Scale: Managing Cross-Functional Teams in Hypergrowth Environments\"\tShows leadership capabilities\tAddresses communication and alignment requirements \"The Cold Email Renaissance: How AI is Revolutionizing B2B Outreach\"\tDemonstrates domain expertise\tDirectly relevant to Instantly.ai's core product \"Building Growth Engines: The Framework for Sustainable SaaS Expansion\"\tShows systematic thinking\tDemonstrates ability to build scalable processes For Account Executive Position: Article Title\tStrategic Positioning\tKey Value Proposition \"The 8-Demo Day: How I Consistently Run 10+ Product Demos Without Burning Out\"\tShows high-volume demo capability\tDirectly addresses key job requirement \"From Cold Outreach to Closed Deals: My 90-Day Sales Acceleration Framework\"\tDemonstrates full-cycle sales expertise\tShows ability to generate own pipeline \"The AI Sales Advantage: How I Increased Close Rates by 40% Using Smart Automation\"\tShows AI product knowledge\tAligns with company's AI focus \"B2B Sales in the Age of AI: Why Human Connection Still Wins Deals\"\tThought leadership in AI sales\tPositions you as industry expert \"The Modern SDR-to-AE Transition: What I Learned Scaling from $500K to $2M Quota\"\tShows career progression\tDemonstrates scalability and growth potential \"Product Demo Mastery: The 5-Step Framework That Converts 60% of Prospects\"\tShows demo expertise\tAddresses core daily responsibility \"Pipeline Generation 2.0: How I Built a $1M Pipeline Using AI-Powered Outreach\"\tShows self-generated pipeline ability\tDemonstrates initiative and results \"The Sales Tech Stack: 12 Tools That Transformed My Sales Performance\"\tShows technical proficiency\tAligns with SaaS sales environment \"From Rejection to Revenue: How I Turned 'No' into $500K in New Business\"\tShows resilience and persistence\tDemonstrates sales mindset \"The Future of B2B Sales: Why Email Automation Platforms Are Game-Changers\"\tIndustry expertise\tDirectly relevant to Instantly.ai's market Innovative Differentiation Strategies 1. Create Interactive Content Experiences Strategy\tImplementation\tExpected Impact Build a Growth Calculator Tool\tCreate a SaaS growth forecasting tool that prospects can use\tDemonstrates technical skills and provides immediate value Design an Email Deliverability Audit\tOffer free email performance analysis using similar methodology to Instantly.ai\tShows domain expertise and adds value to prospects Develop a Sales Pipeline Optimizer\tCreate a tool that helps businesses optimize their sales processes\tPositions you as a strategic thinker with practical skills 2. Thought Leadership Campaigns Strategy\tImplementation\tExpected Impact \"The Daily Growth Experiment\"\tDocument daily growth experiments and results on LinkedIn\tBuilds credibility and shows continuous learning \"SaaS Growth Teardowns\"\tAnalyze successful SaaS companies' growth strategies weekly\tDemonstrates analytical skills and industry knowledge \"Future of Sales\" Video Series\tCreate short-form videos about trends in B2B sales and AI\tIncreases visibility and shows communication skills 3. Direct Value Creation Strategy\tImplementation\tExpected Impact Competitive Analysis Report\tCreate detailed analysis of Instantly.ai vs competitors\tShows initiative and strategic thinking Growth Opportunity Audit\tIdentify 5 untapped growth opportunities for Instantly.ai\tDemonstrates problem-solving and adds immediate value Customer Success Story Framework\tDevelop case study templates for their customer success stories\tShows understanding of their business and adds value LinkedIn Content Strategy for Maximum Impact Content Pillars for Head of Growth: Growth Strategy & Frameworks (40%) Share proven methodologies Case studies from your experience Data-driven insights AI & Automation in Marketing (30%) Tool reviews and comparisons Implementation strategies Future trend predictions Leadership & Team Building (20%) Cross-functional collaboration tips Scaling team experiences Leadership lessons Industry Insights (10%) Market analysis Competitive intelligence Trend commentary Content Pillars for Account Executive: Sales Process & Methodology (40%) Demo techniques Objection handling Closing strategies AI Sales Tools & Technology (30%) Tool reviews Implementation guides ROI case studies Pipeline Development (20%) Outreach strategies Lead qualification Prospecting techniques Personal Sales Stories (10%) Success stories